" ##############
" # MISC PREFS #
" ##############

" Feel free to comment these out if any don't float your boat

"  Change the leader key to <spacebar>
let mapleader=" "

" auto wrap text
set wrap linebreak nolist

" #######
" # GIT #
" #######

" Check spelling and automatically wrap at 72 columns
" (source:https://robots.thoughtbot.com/5-useful-tips-for-a-better-commit-message)
autocmd Filetype gitcommit setlocal spell textwidth=72
